  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, when you say before, you mean during the-- during the part that-- the invasion part?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was in-- the war broke out, and we-- I was, I was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I thought I'd hear about it before the Germans started invading Poland, because we weren't isolated.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were able to hear-- When I say we, I hear-- as a child, you always heard from your elders, during a conversation, during the, the, the time when adults are talking-- what are we going to do?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some were talking about should we leave?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was too late to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some had the opportunity to leave before to the United-- to America, to wherever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some did go, like, prior to the invasion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then a lot of the adults were saying we should have, we could have-- and, and you just hear these things, and you just grow into these things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a child, you're kind of helpless.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, you, you really have no choice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're there, and you wouldn't go anywhere, anyway, because this is your family, your mother, your father, and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was-- there was a preparation for, I would say, today, I know what the time element was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, it'll seem forever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I would say it was-- before the actual [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] takeover, I would say there was about three months of preparations, living under these conditions.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, the Polish government told us to draw the shades and, and, and be careful about exposing ourselves to the bombings and to the-- to the planes that were continually flying over our cities and bombing.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got a pretty good lesson in that endeavor.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
